. These technical failures create severe friction during time-sensitive rebooking situations when trains are cancelled.', '{"original_title" : "Why is Amtrack Website and App such a disaster?", "original_body" : "Train from Philly to NYC on Sat cancelled.  \nWhen I look up \"my trip\" in my account (web) a get a dump of HTML.  \nWhen I go to \"look up my trip\" I''m prompted for e-mail, phone number or booking code - whatever I select - there is no input field.  \nSo website - can''t lookup/find another train.\n\nApp: Found another train. My wife and I grabbed the last two seats in Business class.  \ntried to bid up to first - every time I enter my address and CC info I get bounced out.  \nWTF Amtrack?\n\nIs this usual for Amtrack or are the gods of a the railways dumping on just me today?\n\nEdit: This is the \"My Trips\" page:\n\n[Booooooo](https://preview.redd.it/8tt93kd51u6g1.png?width=1540&format=png&auto=webp&s=244b477c6e7eec77c0e535fb56b63554abdd4768)\n\n", "subreddit" : "r/technology_and_software", "upvotes" : 5, "comments" : 1, "platform" : "reddit", "url" : "", "confidence_score" : 0.85}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL) ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING;
